    "Background": {
      "text": "CMV is part of the Herpesviridae family\n50-80% of the world's population is seropositive for CMV\nCauses a mild or undetectable infection in immunocompetent hosts\nSevere systemic illness is found in immunosuppressed hosts",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Fever\nAnorexia\nMalaise\nAbdominal pain\n, Abdominal distention,\nconstipation\nNausea/vomiting\nChronic watery\ndiarrhea\nBloody diarrhea\nWorsening symptoms of\ninflammatory bowel disease\nWeight loss\nDehydration",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
